profile_summary: This 35-year-old software engineer from Nashville, Tennessee, is currently based in Los Angeles, California. With a graduate education from The University of California, Los Angeles, he values hard work, family, and health & fitness, and is deeply interested in technology, cooking, and outdoor activities. Being a man who goes by the pronouns He/Him/His, he is straight, a white Caucasian, and follows liberal politics. Though he's agnostic, he's a Leo and an INTJ by MBTI personality type. Despite his active lifestyle, he likes to take a drink occasionally, but he's a firm no-smoker and doesn't fancy drugs or marijuana either. He officially states that he doesn't have any children yet but is open to having them in the future. The furry friend he has is a dog. His dating intentions revolve around a long term, monogamous relationship.

The user values hard work, family values, and a penchant for health and fitness in his partner, and an interest in technology, cooking and outdoor activities would mirror his own. English and Spanish speaking is optimal, and she should hold an educational level ranging from undergraduate to doctoral.
